      <param name="text">This dashboard provides a view into the processes running on your virtual desktops. %CPU and memory consumption data is captured for each process. Rare processes are those that occur on fewer than a defined number of virtual machines, and typically represent applications installed by end users. Use the time picker to adjust the time range for the dashboards. Filter this view by Farm, Desktop Catalog, VM name, and Process Name. Clicking on a Proccess name from the table below will bring to the Virtual Desktop sessions running the selected process.  Look at the Resource Reports in the Resource Profiler menu for detailed resource usage reports.
</param>
